<br>
The other day I was in a group with a 61 Necro, 55 SK, 56 Ranger, 55 Cleric and me (61 Mage).  We were hunting the Arachnae Defilers in PoD.  They are almost all 55+, hit pretty darn hard and have a nasty Harmtouch.  There were quite a few &quot;touchy&quot; moments with the SK almost dying from the HT then melee until the first heal landed.  Then the cleric went LD and never came back.  <br>
<br>
For 20 minutes or so until we got a replacement we didn't even have to slow down pulls, we just let the pets tank instead.  The SK would pull close and FD then we would send pets.  My pet took every HT and tanked all of the spiders with just me healing between nukes (only lvl 52 heal) and maybe 1 500pt heal from the necro.  He never got below 40%. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=103898" target="top">Baron Evelle Fyrestrike</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
